      <p class="article-subtitle">不是叫你不要買，是叫你想清楚再買</p>
      <img src="/images/articles/seth2-buy-fg-cover.webp" alt="芭樂子站在戰神賽特2 BUY 按鈕前，周圍環繞倍數球" width="1200" height="669" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" style="display:block;width:100%;max-width:820px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;margin:1rem auto 1.5rem" />

